title: Newly Renovated 3 Bedroom/3 Bath With Panoramic Views !!!!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Large, Glass-Enclosed Indoor Pool, Sauna and Steam Room Open Year Round', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', '-Whirlpool stainless steel appliance suite with French door refrigerator and backless range', '-Certified 100% sprinklered apartments', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', '-The Cyber Lounge Hosts a 24-hr, Self-Serve Coffee Bar, Pool Table and Computer Stations Making This a Great Place to Connect and Recharge', '-Studio+ Highlighting Wellbeats!', 'Offering a Variety of On-Demand Exercise Programs', '-The Event Features a Demonstration Kitchen with Enough Room to Entertain a Few Close Friends or a Crowd', '-Well Equipped Tech Center with Mac and PC Computers and Multi-Function Printer', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
